{"id":273053,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-冯正虎借钱的通报（四）：缴纳罚金二万/","date":"2013-01-06T19:45:48Z","modified":"2013-01-06T19:45:48Z","title":"维权网 | 冯正虎借钱的通报（四）：缴纳罚金二万元","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>日</span><span>，冯正虎完成缴清罚金的十万元借款额，宣布停止借钱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>借钱开始，冯正虎就用邮政特快专递于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMS</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EW386403095CS</span><span>）、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMS</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EW386403033CS</span><span>）、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMS</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EX018104010CS</span><span>）向上海第二中级法院执行庭张法官汇报收入变动的情况，并提出缴纳罚金的申请。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>用邮政特快专递（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMS</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EX018103990CS</span><span>）再次致函上海第二中级法院执行庭张法官转呈院长王信芳，告知愿意缴清冤案的罚金，并要求法院依法解冻冯正虎的银行账户并取款。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>根据法院张法官电话约定，冯正虎于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span><span>到上海市第二中级法院缴纳罚金。张法官与一位年轻的女书记员与冯正虎谈话，并做了笔录。谈话的基本内容：确认冯正虎是用借款缴纳罚金，当场缴纳二万元现金，其余缴纳罚金的钱款在被冻结的冯正虎账户里，冯正虎要求法院依法解除冻结账户并取款。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>与法官会见谈话后，在书记员的带领下向法院财务室缴纳二万元人民币，并拿到收据。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>图：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>冯正虎缴纳罚金二万元人民币的收据</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7MDZ7bN3Frw/UOmmcqlhfPI/AAAAAAAAYUY/tuAHnPgOv8w/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"167\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7MDZ7bN3Frw/UOmmcqlhfPI/AAAAAAAAYUY/tuAHnPgOv8w/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}